        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> Is that shell script at the root of the project?\n\nYes, that's right. It's in the root of the project because it reaches into aai-schema-gen and aai-schema sub-directories during the run.\n\nThere might be better places to put it, esp. if we try to integrate it into the pom.xml as an extra maven goal to re-generate diagrams (I was looking at a plantuml-maven plugin but it appears to be unmaintained for the last couple years).",
